        <updateDate>2008-02-08T15:20:20Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Giving Resources and Opportunities to the Workforce Act of 2008 - Amends the Internal Revenue Code to: (1) allow a five-year carryback for net operating losses incurred in 2007, 2008, or 2009; and (2) increase to $250,000 in 2008 the expensing allowance for certain depreciable business assets. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
